CALL ME MADAM 2019 ENCORES! At New York City Center

Produced by ENCORES! At New York City Center

Book by Howard Lindsay and Russel Crouse; Music by Irving Berlin; Musical Director: Rob Berman

Directed by Casey Hushion; Choreography by Denis Jones

Scenic Design by Allan Moyer; Costume Design by Jennifer Caprio; Lighting Design by Jason Lyons; Sound Design by Scott Lehrer; Hair and Wig Design by Josh Marquette

Starring Carmen Cusack as Ambassador Sally Adams, Ben Davis as Cosmo Constantine, Jason Gotay as Kenneth Gibson, Adam Heller as Congressman Wilkins, Carol Kane as Grand Duchess Sophie, Darrell Hammond as Grand Duke Otto, Stanley Wayne Mathis as Senator Brockbank, Tony nominee Brad Oscar as Senator Gallagher, Michael Benjamin Washington as Pemberton Maxwell, and Tony nominee Lauren Worsham as Princess Maria.

Also including Florrie Bagel, Daniel Berryman, Taeler Elyse Cyrus, Leslie Flesner, Ta’Nika Gibson, Christopher Gurr, Leah Horowitz, Javier Ignacio, Max Kumangai, Matt Loehr, Brandt Martinez, Skye Mattox, Timothy McDevitt, Harris Milgrim, Bethany Moore, Mary Page Nance, Randy Rainbow, Robert Roby, Kathy Voytko, Sumi Yu, and Ricardo Zayas.
